text: "Over Now" is a 1996 song by Alice in Chains. It was taken from their live album Unplugged. It went to number 50 in Canada and number 4 on the Billboard Mainstream Rock chart. It was also on their greatest hits album The Essential Alice in Chains in 2006. The album version was taken from their 1995 album Alice in Chains. ==Track listing== Category:1996 songs Category:Alice in Chains songs Category:Acoustic rock songs Category:Alternative rock songs
